column2: SELECT so.bestObjID,so.specObjID, so.ra, so.dec,nd.ra as Gal_ra,nd.dec as Gal_dec,so.plate, so.mjd, so.fiberID, elp.Flux_Hb_#, elp.AoN_Hb_#, elp.Flux_NII_#,elp.FLUX_OIII_#, elp.AoN_NII_#, elp.Flux_Ha_#, elp.AoN_Ha_#,elp.AoN_OIII_#, elp.Flux_HeII_#, elp.AoN_HeII_#, so.z, so.snMedian, elp.V_Hb_#,elp.V_NII_#,elp.V_Ha_#,elp.V_OIII_#, elp.Flux_OI_#,elp.AoN_OI_#,elp.Flux_SII_#,elp.AoN_SII_#,elp.Flux_SII_#,elp.AoN_SII_#,elp.V_SII_#,elp.V_SII_#,elp.V_OI_#,elp.bpt,elp.V_HeII_# into mydb.Nucdwarf_sn from MyDB.Nuc_dwarfs as nd CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(nd.ra,nd.dec,#) as w JOIN SpecObjAll so ON so.bestObjID = w.objID JOIN emissionLinesPort as elp ON so.specObjid = elp.specObjid
